- # Shown when a student's JoinCourse fails for an unexpected reason (the
- # unbound and awaiting-approval cases have their own views). Styled like the
- # other in-iframe landings, with a re-launch retry for when the underlying
- # issue clears; the contact hint lives in the explanation copy.
.lti-iframe__landing
  = image_tag '/assets/images/wiki-logo.png', alt: 'Wiki Education Dashboard', class: 'lti-iframe__logo'
  %h3.lti-iframe__title= t('lti.enrollment_error.header')
  %p= t('lti.enrollment_error.explanation')
  -# Re-launches in the iframe so the student can retry once the issue is
  -# resolved, without having to know to reload the Canvas tab.
  = link_to t('lti.check_again'), "/lti?ltik=#{CGI.escape(params[:ltik].to_s)}",
            class: 'lti-iframe__check-again'
